snippet: Samantha Stosur, the defending champion, will move on to play Laura Robson of Britain, who has beaten Li Na and Kim Clijsters at this United States Open.
abstract: Laura Robson defeats Li Na in three sets to earn a spot in the fourth round of the United States Open; other tournament results noted.
lead_paragraph: Samantha Stosur, the defending champion, will move on to play Laura Robson of Britain, who has beaten Li Na and Kim Clijsters at this United States Open.

headline.seo: U.S. Open - Robson Knocks Off Another Seed to Gain Fourth Round
headline.main: Robson Knocks Off Another Seed to Reach the Fourth Round
headline.print_headline: Robson Knocks Off Another Seed to Reach the Fourth Round
